because I have more experience
in the project, in the code,

00:42:29.130 --> 00:42:30.660
while he may have
more experience

00:42:30.660 --> 00:42:31.930
professionally, long term.

00:42:31.930 --> 00:42:32.730
BRIAN FITZPATRICK: How many
people on the team?

00:42:32.730 --> 00:42:33.010
